  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/cany/index.htm",
  "description": "Canyonlands is a wilderness of canyons, buttes, and spires carved by the Colorado River and Green River. The park is divided into four distinct districts; no roads join them together. The districts share similar desert ecosystems, but each one provides unique opportunities for adventure and discovery.",
  "designation": "National Park",
  "states": [
